### ============================================
### Dent-in API — REST Client Test File
### ============================================
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code.
### Click "Send Request" above any block below.
### ============================================

### ---- HEALTH CHECK ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dentists

### ---- REGISTER ----
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fullName": "Test User",
    "email": "test@dentin.health",
    "phone": "+62 811 9999 000",
    "address": null,
    "dateOfBirth": null,
    "gender": null,
    "emergencyContact": null,
    "medicalHistory": null,
    "password": "password123"
}

### ---- LOGIN ----
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "identifier": "test@dentin.health",
    "password": "password123"
}

### ---- SEND OTP ----
POST http://localhost:8080/api/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@dentin.health",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### ---- VERIFY OTP (replace CODE with 6-digit code from console) ----
POST http://localhost:8080/api/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@dentin.health",
    "code": "000000",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### ---- GET PATIENTS ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients

### ---- GET DENTISTS ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dentists

### ---- GET DENTIST BY ID ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dentists/1

### ---- GET ACTIVE DENTISTS ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dentists/active

### ---- MAP: GET API KEY ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maps/api-key

### ---- MAP: GET ALL LOCATIONS ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maps/locations

### ---- MAP: NEARBY (Jakarta) ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maps/nearby?lat=-6.2088&lng=106.8456&radiusKm=10

### ---- MAP: DIRECTIONS ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maps/directions?lat=-6.2088&lng=106.8456

### ---- CREATE APPOINTMENT ----
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "patientId": 1,
    "dentistId": 1,
    "appointmentDate": "2026-07-20",
    "appointmentTime": "14:30",
    "reason": "Root canal follow-up",
    "notes": "Booked via Dent-in"
}

### ---- GET APPOINTMENTS BY PATIENT ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/patient/1

### ---- GET PRESCRIPTIONS BY PATIENT ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prescriptions/patient/1

### ---- GET NOTIFICATIONS BY PATIENT ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/patient/1

### ---- GET UNREAD NOTIFICATION COUNT ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/patient/1/count

### ---- GET SCANS BY PATIENT ----
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scans/patient/1

### ---- H2 CONSOLE ----
### Open in browser: http://localhost:8080/h2-console
### JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:dentaldb
### User: sa
### Password: (empty)

### ---- SWAGGER UI ----
### Open in browser: http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
